# miniobj
Minimum wavefront .obj file parser in Python

## Installation
```bash
pip install miniobj
```

## Usage
```python
from miniobj import MiniObjLoader

loader = MiniObjLoader("mesh.obj")
loader.load()
```

Check out [main.py](main.py) for more examples.
